    "description": "Draft Fever Bowl 是一款竞争激烈的<strong>足球管理模拟</strong>游戏。<strong>侦察</strong>潜力球员、进行战略性的<strong>线上交易</strong>，并在<strong>选秀</strong>中竞争明星球员。每个决定都至关重要！<br><br>提升排名，获得 Fever Bowl 的资格，并争夺最终的荣耀！踏上球场，通过完全3D和逼真的比赛引擎观察你的名单运作！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100820/extras/487c77ad07089972c11bacc3697ab574.avif?t=1765835388\" width=616 height=96 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选秀球员！</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100820/extras/c04b9b89b237a2646ed90224fa47cde9.poster.avif?t=1765835388\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100820/extras/c04b9b89b237a2646ed90224fa47cde9.webm?t=1765835388\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100820/extras/c04b9b89b237a2646ed90224fa47cde9.mp4?t=1765835388\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>参与我们每周更新的全面和沉浸式选秀系统。制定战略以确保最佳选择，侦察超过100所大学，发现隐藏的宝石来提升你的名单。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >观看比赛！</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100820/extras/2b01dd8816547e95d2d816366a8c636a.poster.avif?t=1765835388\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100820/extras/2b01dd8816547e95d2d816366a8c636a.webm?t=1765835388\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100820/extras/2b01dd8816547e95d2d816366a8c636a.mp4?t=1765835388\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>通过我们先进的3D比赛模拟引擎，见证比赛的刺激。观看你的球队在场上展示各自的技能和团队合作，每个球员都生动地展现出来。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >进行线上交易</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100820/extras/ea0cf1aa9a344d8e434f627f5ccfc985.poster.avif?t=1765835388\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100820/extras/ea0cf1aa9a344d8e434f627f5ccfc985.webm?t=1765835388\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100820/extras/ea0cf1aa9a344d8e434f627f5ccfc985.mp4?t=1765835388\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>体验一个稳健的交易系统，允许你与其他用户协商并交易选秀权和球员。你的球员是独特的可收藏卡片，你可以在激动人心的比赛模拟中观察他们的表现。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >组建你的队伍！</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100820/extras/91d4c420f3cde8b4fb898422800b2b44.poster.avif?t=1765835388\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100820/extras/91d4c420f3cde8b4fb898422800b2b44.webm?t=1765835388\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100820/extras/91d4c420f3cde8b4fb898422800b2b44.mp4?t=1765835388\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>通过组建最佳球员和制定获胜策略来建立和管理你的梦之队。专注于团队协同和战术深度，以确保胜利并在竞争排名中上升。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >即时事件！</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100820/extras/1cba9c869b5fee0f1af2b3e3e2998d3a.poster.avif?t=1765835388\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100820/extras/1cba9c869b5fee0f1af2b3e3e2998d3a.webm?t=1765835388\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100820/extras/1cba9c869b5fee0f1af2b3e3e2998d3a.mp4?t=1765835388\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>沉浸在 &quot;Draft Fever Bowl&quot; 的动态世界中，游戏事件与现实时间同步。赛季、锦标赛、比赛和选秀之夜被安排为现场活动。实时或异步参与，确保你不会错过任何精彩的行动。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100820/extras/e84a6c31456eb62d0c1425646bf721e4.avif?t=1765835388\" width=616 height=120 /></span>",
